*[http://www.alpertron.com.ar/ECM.HTM Fast Online primality test with factorization]{{Wayback|url=http://www.alpertron.com.ar/ECM.HTM |date=20090910074733 }} makes use of the Elliptic Curve Method (up to thousand-digits numbers, requires Java).
